chat.msg: hola, you ready?
yes
sweet
i'm starting at the twig, just left of a small island with a tiger. which way now?
head southwest
alright, i see a big island with a parrot sitting on a tree
now what?
go aroujnd the parrow and off to your left and south towards the elephant
cool, passed the parrot, and i'm now with the elephant
where to next, boss?
head south and off to the right, or esat, towards a set or rocks to cross over to next island where you will see a frog
gotcha! passed the rocks, and i see the frog on a small island
what's next?
head south of the frog then take a sharp left, heading west
alrighty, took a sharp left
now i'm seeing the crocodile and the elephant again. where to now?
continue left, or west, , passing over crocodile. pass over a black rock and continue under elephant towards grey rocks that wikll bring you to a new island with a giaraffe visible
done and dusted
i've passed the crocodile, crossed the black rock and i'm now at the giraffe's island. what next?
head directlyl south and take a right to cross over to anew island where you will encounter a pretty snake
got it! i'm past the giraffe and now at snake's location
where to now?
pass the snake by continuing to your right, or east and you will arrive at a treasure chest
bro, you're a star! i've passed the snake and now i'm at the treasure
*finished*
hola, q tal? ready to start?
sure am
great! start by going left, just below the wooden bench, until you cross a trail
but stop before you reach the florist stand, okay?
yes
cool! now, i want you to make a u-turn to your left, cross the trail again
you'll see a familiar doggy face, head back to it
ok
right on! now it's time to cross the branch that's just to your south
then, continue to go down the map
ok
great job! now you're near another white dog, aren't you? that fella's having a picnic. from there, i want you to go west
step over the picnic mat and walk close to that bowl of berries. give the berries a sniff, they smell good, don't they?
yes
neat! now, see that wooden branch just ahead? walk over it bringing you north
cross the river. you're doing great!
ok
once you're over, i want you to go around that green bush on your right
don't touch it, just admire from afar
ok
nice! now, head towards that florist stand you saw earlier
remember? it should be right there
yes
woohoo! now let's jog a little to the left under the stand
ok
and keep going until you see a big bridge with two cyclists
isn't it beautiful? go past it
ok
and there you'll find two old pals reading newspapers
just beyond the bridge. wave hello to them!
ok
now, a few steps to the south between our friends and the branch should lead you to a new acquaintance
deer
ah, no spoilers! but keep walking towards that green bush next to the end of the wooden branch where i mentioned our new friend might be
ok
perfect! now take the path between the branch and the bush heading east
almost there!
hi there, empezamos?
yes
perfect! right now I'm in the store up north
where should i start?
head east, to your right
you got it, mate! i see a fire with a pooch chilling to the left
what's next?
head north
uh oh, looks like i'm at a dead end
sure it wasn't south?
sorry got lost of where store is, head south under dog and over fire,continue south
no worries! okay, i've passed the fire cosily sitting right of the dog
i see a red mushroom and a blue car ahead. which one should i go towards?
go towards mushroom but head under it towards card, take south a short bit and then head west awway from car
gotcha! i'm passing by this weird red mushroom and heading towards the blue car
alright, i see a telescope more south from here and some rocks to the west
head towards telescope, staying to the left (or west) of it, go under telescope then head towards rocks, staying under them
roger that! i'm going past the telescope now and keeping these rocks within my sight
head towards log cabin on your left to your west
okay, i'm heading towards the cabin now
whoa, we've reached the wooden house! *finished*
hola, you ready?
yes
awesome! starting at those three palm trees, scoot towards the south-west underneath the first tree, then make a quick right and pass the second tree
then swerve hard to your left before you hit tree number three and tread southwards. got it?
yes
cool beans! now, take a few strides and head slightly left, passing to the left of a little brown pup
then smooth turn right, moving south. let me know when you're there
ok
perfect! now, see that big rock to your left and the small one to your right? glide straight through that gap and you'll hit the water
tell me when you're soaking
wet
ha! you're a trooper
ok, now you're gonna need to veer right at our crabby friend, making a dash westwards along the big rock. stay in the surf for now - it's part of the fun!
lost
no sweat! remember the large red crab we mentioned? once you see that, stay in the water and turn right, heading west but keeping close to the big rock
you're doing great!
right is not west
you're right! my bad
so, you're facing the crab, right? now, take a turn westwards which should be to your left if you're facing the crab. keep hugging the big rock
ok
awesome job! now keep going until you spot a medium-sized rock
yes
great!  now when you see a shark, don't panic, just take a sharp right turn
don't get bit!
ok
you're playing this like a pro! time to get out of the water, head back to the land by moving between the medium rock and a soccer ball with blue, yellow and white patches
head northwards after that
ok
fantastic! from there, take a soft left turn heading north-west
you're going to pass between a party red tent on your left and a boss size speaker on your right
ok
good job! circle around the tent in an arc and then make your way south towards the sea again
ok
Phew! almost there. but don't dive back in
just at the shore, see right (that's west for you) and maneuver under a fiery red kayak. you're doing fantastic!
ok
okay, okay, final stretch! now turn a clear 90 degrees to your right (that's north)
ok
and follow the edge of the kayak until you reach a small green bush
you are crushing it!
